---
interface Props {}
---
<section class="relative py-stack-xl h-screen flex items-center bg-on-background text-white overflow-hidden" id="experiencia" aria-labelledby="experiencia-title">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img
      alt="Interior da Di Napoli: tijolinhos aparentes, teto alto de madeira, iluminação pendente industrial quente, assentos de couro confortáveis, grandes janelas com luz natural"
      class="parallax-img opacity-40 brightness-50"
      src="/assets/ambiente.webp"
      loading="eager"
      width="1920"
      height="1080"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="container-main relative z-10 w-full">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-stack-xl items-center">
      <div>
        <span class="font-ui-label text-primary-fixed uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[10px] mb-8 inline-block mask-reveal active">Nossa Atmosfera</span>
        <h2 id="experiencia-title" class="font-display-lg text-6xl leading-[1.1] mb-stack-lg mask-reveal active">Aconchego em <br /><span class="italic">cada detalhe.</span></h2>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md mb-12 blur-reveal active" style="transition-delay: 300ms">
          Materiais nobres, luz suave e trilha sonora cuidadosamente curada. Criamos o refúgio perfeito para suas conversas mais importantes ou seus momentos de introspecção.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-12 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 border-t border-white/10 pt-12 blur-reveal active" style="transition-delay: 500ms">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
            Pet Friendly
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
            Coworking Space
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
            Kids Area
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>